Package: sectioncomment
Type: Package
Title: Create Clean Section Break Comments
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Steven", "Mortimer", email = "reportmort@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Creates an 80 character width comment padded with hyphens, similar to how comments are shown in Hadley's style guide (http://adv-r.had.co.nz/Style.html)
URL: https://github.com/reportmort/sectioncomment
BugReports: https://github.com/reportmort/sectioncomment/issues
Depends:
  R (>= 3.2.0)
Imports:
  stringr (>= 1.0.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
